HEADWORD: Filiety
<hw>Fi*li"e*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>filietas</ets>.]</ety> <def>The relation of a son to a father;
sonship; -- the correlative of <xex>paternity</xex>.</def> <rj><au>J. S.
Mill.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

